n type of icon. </Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SCENE ID</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TEXT ID</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENGLISH STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LOCALIZED STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALTERNATIVE ENGLISH STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALTERNATIVE LOCALIZED STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LOCALIZATION NOTES</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DEV TEAM / MISC NOTES</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">CELESTIAN_SKILL_GROUP</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SKILL_SUBTITLE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Celestian Hero Skill</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Umiejętność bohatera Niebian</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill tree header. 
Celestian is an in-game secret tech.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">REVEALING_SOUL</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Revealing Soul</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Obnażenie duszy</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="75"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">REVEALING_SOUL</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Hero gains [abilityblue]Enlightened[/abilityblue], and all units that attack the hero have a strength {RevealingSoulStrength}[StrengthPsyche/] chance of being afflicted with [abilityred]Soulburn[/abilityred].</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Bohater jest [abilityblue]oświecony[/abilityblue]. Wszystkie jednostki, które go zaatakują, mają szansę ({RevealingSoulStrength}[StrengthPsyche/] siły) na to, że zostaną [abilityred]potępione[/abilityred].</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.
Enlightened is an in-game buff, Soulburn is a debuff.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="60"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">REVEALING_SOUL</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION_SHIELD</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Enemies that attack this unit have a strength {RevealingSoulStrength}[StrengthPsyche/] chance of being afflicted with [abilityred]Soulburn[/abilityred].</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Wrogowie, którzy zaatakują tę jednostkę, mają szansę ({RevealingSoulStrength}[StrengthPsyche/] siły) na to, że zostaną [abilityred]potępieni[/abilityred].</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Unit buff description.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">AURA_OF_GUIDANCE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Aura of Guidance</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Boskie naprowadzanie</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="60"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">AURA_OF_GUIDANCE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Every unit in the hero's army has {AuraOfGuidanceAcc} increased accuracy.[br/]Only functions when the hero is the army's commander.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Wszystkie jednostki w armii bohatera mają celność zwiększoną o {AuraOfGuidanceAcc}.[br/]Możliwe tylko wtedy, gdy ten bohater jest dowódcą armii.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.
Commander in this context means the leader of an army, NOT the player character</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">AURA_OF_GUIDANCE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION_UNIT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{AuraOfGuidanceAcc} increased accuracy.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Celność zwiększona o {AuraOfGuidanceAcc}.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Unit buff description.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DENY_THE_WICKED</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Deny the Wicked</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Odtrącenie niegodziwców</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="105"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DENY_THE_WICKED</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Every unit in the hero's army has {DenyTheWickedReduction} damage reduction in all channels against attacks from units with [abilityred]Soulburn[/abilityred].[br/]Only functions when the hero is the army's commander.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Wszystkie jednostki w armii bohatera otrzymują od [abilityred]potępionych[/abilityred] jednostek obrażenia zmniejszone o {DenyTheWickedReduction} na wszystkich kanałach.[br/]Możliwe tylko wtedy, gdy ten bohater jest dowódcą armii.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.
Channels in this case are damage channels, as in different types of damage (thermal, bio)
Commander in this context means the leader of an army, NOT the player character</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DENY_THE_WICKED</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION_UNIT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Unit has {DenyTheWickedReduction} damage reduction in all channels against units with [abilityred]Soulburn[/abilityred].</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Jednostka otrzymuje obrażenia od [abilityred]potępionych[/abilityred] jednostek zmniejszone o {DenyTheWickedReduction} na wszystkich kanałach.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Unit buff description.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">COMPELLING_PRESENCE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Compelling Presence</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Dominująca obecność</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Text between {} should NOT be localized as they are numerical values in-game. Text between [] should NOT be localized as they are either icons or text formatting

